# =============================================================================
# .gitignore — EngageTown VAST Challenge 2022 MC1
# =============================================================================
# 原则：追踪源代码和分析结果，忽略原始数据、中间产物和运行时可生成文件。
# 详见 README.md "Git 工作流程" 章节。

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Python
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.egg-info/
.eggs/
*.egg
*.so
dist/
build/

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Virtual environments
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
venv/
.venv/
env/
.env
.venv-*

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# IDE / Editor
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
*.sublime-*

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# OS generated files
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Claude Code session files (local only)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
.claude/

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Jupyter
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
.ipynb_checkpoints/
*.ipynb

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Streamlit
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
.streamlit/secrets.toml

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 原始数据集（~3GB，可由 process_data.py 重新生成 processed/）
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
Datasets/

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 处理后的 Parquet 中间文件（由 process_data.py 生成，约 1.3MB）
# 克隆后运行 `python process_data.py` 即可重新生成
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
processed/
*.parquet

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 测试与调试
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
*.log
*.tmp
.pytest_cache/
coverage.xml
.coverage
htmlcov/

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 其他
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
*.bak
*.orig
